in a rare show of unity ruling and 
opposition lawmakers today approved without debate legislation that 
will raise their salaries by 85 percent on jan 1 
the twominute action raised a lawmakers monthly salary from the 
current 2550 to 4730 bringing their pay to the level of cabinet 
ministers 
the bill was approved by the national assemblys budget 
settlement committee its passage by the full assembly will be a 
mere formality 
many south koreans criticized the steep pay increase as 
unethical citing the meager incomes of most factory workers and 
high inflation 
according to industry figures a footwear assembly line worker 
with five years of job experience makes about 550 a month 
including allowances 
