during the protest saturday in lhasa the tibetan capital in which 
chinese officials said a tibetan buddhist monk was killed 
western witnesses said they saw two bodies including that of a 
small child and that tibetans told them seven people were killed 
li said ms meindersma also violated customs regulations by 
bringing into lhasa a book by the dalai lama tibets exiled former 
leader the book my land and my people is banned in china 
because it advocates tibets independence from china 
