ms meindersma but willem de bruin adminstrative and consular 
attache at the dutch embassy said today that authorities told him 
no charges would be filed 
li did not acknowledge that ms meindersma was shot by police 
and only spoke of her being slightly injured she said a bullet 
entered her left arm and exited through her shoulder 
tibetan activists seeking the return of the dalai lama and an end 
to 38 years of chinese communist rule have demonstrated repeatedly 
over the past 14 months saturdays confrontation was the third 
protest to end in bloodshed 
