president reagan said today he would not 
hesitate to break off communications with the palestine 
liberation organization if it reneged on its declarations to 
renounce terrorism and accept israels right to exist 
reagan defended his decision to permit a dialogue between us 
officials and yasser arafats plo reversing a 12year us 
