to usisraeli strategic cooperation and he said he would not deal 
with the plo or back an independent palestinian state echoing 
administration positions of the day 
it remains to be seen whether reagan and shultzs legacy to bush 
and baker will be a blessing or a curse 
asked thursday if he would prefer that the talks wait until his 
administration starts next month bush replied i become president 
on jan 20 on jan 21 ill tell you what i want to do 
