thursday to the us declaration that it will talk with the plo a 
stunning reversal of policy to which they were given no time to 
object 
some israelis were left with a sense of betrayal by the way the 
announcement was handled others said the dialogue with the 
palestine liberation organization is doomed to collapse 
we believe that the united states will discover very soon the 
true face of the plo and will realize that it cannot be a partner 
for negotiations and peace said avi pazner spokesman for prime 
