israelis see as a forum for demanding unreasonable concessions from 
the jewish state 
a conference probably would consider such issues as the israeli 
settlements that dot the occupied territories return of the 
territories the status of jerusalem and the central question of an 
independent palestinian state 
an example of what israel considers unreasonable was a provision 
